---
---

<section class="p-village" id="village">
  <div class="u-section">
    <div class="p-village__header js-fade-up">
      <p class="p-village__label">ABOUT</p>
      <h2 class="p-village__title">信州高山村について</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="p-village__layout">
      <div class="p-village__img js-fade-up">
        <img src="/images/village.svg" alt="高山村の風景" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="p-village__content js-fade-up">
        <p class="p-village__text">長野県の北部、須坂市の東隣に位置する高山村。南アルプスを望む標高700mの高原は、昼夜の寒暖差が大きく、果樹栽培に最適な環境です。澄んだ空気と豊かな水が、ここでしか出せない味わいを育みます。</p>
        <div class="p-village__stats">
          <div class="p-village__stat">
            <span class="p-village__stat-num">700m</span>
            <span class="p-village__stat-label">標高</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-village__stat">
            <span class="p-village__stat-num">15℃以上</span>
            <span class="p-village__stat-label">寒暖差</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-village__stat">
            <span class="p-village__stat-num">10年</span>
            <span class="p-village__stat-label">栽培歴</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-village__stat">
            <span class="p-village__stat-num">10+</span>
            <span class="p-village__stat-label">品種数</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
